title: Error converting from coreml: "Unsupported shape calculation for operator expandDims"
body:
Got error when trying to convert my .mlmodel to onnx model following onnxmltools documentation: https://github.com/onnx/onnxmltools#coreml-to-onnx-conversion

```python
import onnxmltools
import coremltools

# Load a Core ML model
coreml_model = coremltools.utils.load_spec('hands.mlmodel')

# Convert the Core ML model into ONNX
onnx_model = onnxmltools.convert_coreml(coreml_model, 'Hands Pose Model')

# Save as protobuf
onnxmltools.utils.save_model(onnx_model, 'hands.onnx')
```

Here in this line exactly:
```python
onnx_model = onnxmltools.convert_coreml(coreml_model, 'Hands Pose Model')
```

Error:
```
Traceback (most recent call last):
  File "<stdin>", line 1, in <module>
  File "/Users/rmaja/opt/miniconda3/envs/coreml/lib/python3.6/site-packages/onnxmltools/convert/main.py", line 18, in convert_coreml
    custom_conversion_functions, custom_shape_calculators)
  File "/Users/rmaja/opt/miniconda3/envs/coreml/lib/python3.6/site-packages/onnxmltools/convert/coreml/convert.py", line 57, in convert
    topology = parse_coreml(spec, initial_types, target_opset, custom_conversion_functions, custom_shape_calculators)
  File "/Users/rmaja/opt/miniconda3/envs/coreml/lib/python3.6/site-packages/onnxmltools/convert/coreml/_parse.py", line 463, in parse_coreml
    topology.compile()
  File "/Users/rmaja/opt/miniconda3/envs/coreml/lib/python3.6/site-packages/onnxconverter_common/topology.py", line 678, in compile
    self._infer_all_types()
  File "/Users/rmaja/opt/miniconda3/envs/coreml/lib/python3.6/site-packages/onnxconverter_common/topology.py", line 553, in _infer_all_types
    operator.infer_types()
  File "/Users/rmaja/opt/miniconda3/envs/coreml/lib/python3.6/site-packages/onnxconverter_common/topology.py", line 107, in infer_types
    get_shape_calculator(self.type)(self)
  File "/Users/rmaja/opt/miniconda3/envs/coreml/lib/python3.6/site-packages/onnxconverter_common/registration.py", line 67, in get_shape_calculator
    raise ValueError('Unsupported shape calculation for operator %s' % operator_name)
ValueError: Unsupported shape calculation for operator expandDims
```

Environment:
- macOS 12.3.1
- python 3.6.9
- coremltools==5.2.0 (latest version)
- onnxmltools==1.11.0 (latest version)

Thanks,
